allMeta.bullet_short_copy:
• Nearly indestructible and totally reliable design
  • Corrosion- and weather-resistant
  • Multiple integrated safety features
  • Two magazines and a hard-plastic case included
allMeta.description: Glock polymer-frame, fixed-sight pistols have seen military, security and law-enforcement duty across the globe. Known for being nearly indestructible and totally reliable, theyre also popular with civilian shooters. Light, durable, oil- and corrosion-resistant polymer frames are mated to steel slides. The harder-than-steel slides are treated with a nonreflecting, rust-resistant Tennifer-coating. Hexagonal barrel profiles result in longer service life and easy cleaning. Loaded-chamber indicators confirm the presence of chambered rounds by sight and touch. Glocks Safe Action System controls three internal safeties, including a drop safety that prevents discharge if the gun is dropped. Each pistol comes with a pair of magazines and a hard-plastic case.
allMeta.title: Glock Standard-Frame Fixed-Sight Pistols
